title: Weirdhouse Cinema: Plan 9 from Outer Space
itunes:title: Weirdhouse Cinema: Plan 9 from Outer Space
description:
In this episode of Weirdhouse Cinema, Rob and Joe finally discuss a film that almost defies description: “Plan 9 From Outer Space.” Yes, it’s Ed Wood’s 1957 cinematic monolith featuring Bela Lugosi, Tor Johnson, Vampira and the Amazing Criswell!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
